enixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emaylindstrom.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eSocial Media: \u003ca href=\"http://instagram.com/maylindstromskin/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"http://www.facebook.com/maylindstromskin\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat:\u003c/strong\u003e A small-batch \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin-care\u003c/a\u003e brand that offers cleansing oils, facial serums, masks and body oils that rely on natural ingredients\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range:\u003c/strong\u003e $75-$220\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounder:\u003c/strong\u003e May Lindstrom\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story:\u003c/strong\u003e May Lindstrom founded her eponymous skin-care brand in 2011 after a lifelong struggle with highly sensitive and reactive skin. With traditional \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin care\u003c/a\u003e and many \u0026#34;natural\u0026#34; ingredients irritating Lindstrom\u0026#39;s skin, she began immersing herself in the study of plant medicine and began creating her own formulas to target her specific needs. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMay Lindstrom manufactures its products in small batches in-house and formulates with \u0026#34;healing plants, medicinal herbs, spices, mineral salts and clays.\u0026#34; The brand\u0026#39;s mission is \u0026#34;to provide a catalyst for a conscious time-out, while also delivering unparalleled personal service and measurable results.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-